dcterms:creator: Y. LeCun
dcterms:description: A well-known dataset of handwritten digits, consisting of 60,000 training images and 10,000 testing images, each of size 28x28 pixels. The dataset is used for training various machine learning models, particularly in the field of image recognition.
dcterms:title: MNIST

dcterms:description: A dataset consisting of fashion items, designed to serve as a drop-in replacement for the MNIST dataset, containing 60,000 training images and 10,000 testing images of clothing items.
dcterms:title: Fashion MNIST

dcterms:creator: C. Zöllner

R. Schubotz
N. Axmacher
O. T. Wolf
dcterms:description: An experimental dataset used to study the interplay of episodic memory traces and semantic knowledge during scenario construction, involving participants recalling the locations of objects in a virtual environment.
dcterms:title: Zöllner et al. Experiment
